      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 6-speed manual transmission. The vehicle has undergone critical subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul to ensure optimal variable valve timing performance. Power is delivered through a factory limited-slip differential, providing exceptional lateral grip and chassis balance. The suspension geometry remains true, with refreshed bushings and dampers that maintain the sharp turn-in characteristics synonymous with the M-division. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, this example offers a linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline, making it a mechanically robust choice for any serious driving enthusiast.",
